latestPosts.caption:
From @himadri.giri calling me 'so annoying' in PG to surprising me with a 'Happy Anniversary'—who would have thought our friendship would grow this deep? I am beyond grateful to the universe for blessing me with a relationship so meaningful, one I’ll carry with me forever❤️
I love how you always tell the story of how we became friends, especially when you share it with my husband, your eyes lighting up with joy. Thank you for keeping the promise to be a part of every small and big moment in our lives💕
I love you so much! 😘 

Ps. To Papa's Adopted Daughter, my Sibling's Best Friend, my Husband's Business Partner and my Forever Home❤️

“Better late than never, right? ❄️✨ 

Finally sharing glimpses of our winter special moments—because good things take time!

Super proud to introduce @project_warmsouls , our women-led initiative that’s been over a year in the making. With the dedication of skilled artisans from Haryana and Uttarakhand, we’re bringing handwoven fashion back in style, one piece at a time!

Last winter was just the beginning, and we made it a hit! 🙌🏼 Stay tuned—more stories and updates are coming soon on our official page!”

latestPosts.caption:
"Season’s Greetings! 🎉 Stepping into the New Year with a heart bursting with happiness and excitement for all the adventures to come! 🌟 Let’s make it magical, unforgettable, and filled with love and laughter! 💕✨

Reel Credit @ar.un9992

 #NewYearJoy #GratefulHeart #AdventuresAhead"

As India’s festive days depart,
I pen this post with a wistful heart.
To cherish the glow, the vibrant attire,
Moments draped in hues that inspire.

A glimpse of grace, a timeless art,
My Indian look, a soulful part.
Though the season fades, the memories stay,
A treasure of beauty, come what may.

-Himadri

latestPosts.caption:
Edited captures, yet no filters reveal,
Solo travels, a liberating feel.
Once shared with friends, love by your side,
Now you wander alone, on this personal ride.

Each step a balance of light and of weight,
In solitude’s embrace, you navigate fate.
The essence of journeys lies in the quest,
To make the most of each moment, to truly invest.

-Himadri
